Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:15.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:18.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:24.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:39.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:46.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:54.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:01:01.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:08.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:15.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:22.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:33.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:39.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:41.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An egg... An egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:50.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An egg... An egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:52.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:03.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:15.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:19.87,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5\NSecret Plan, The Blue Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:24.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did this come to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the second prince, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:42.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:45.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The second queen was\Nquite clever, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:49.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were hired to be\Nthis boy's bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torogai, this boy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how lucky I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that something\Nthat might appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...only once in a hundred years\Nwould fall into my lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a quick look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What we're dealing with here\Nis an egg, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:25.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've only heard stories\Nabout these until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I'd see one\Nwith my own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Interacting with Nayug is\Nindeed no easy matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master, what in the world is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:51.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the egg of Nyunga Ro Im.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:52.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:55.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is a...whatever you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:04:00.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Nyunga Ro Im is a creature said\Nto drink the waters of Sagu dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's what the people of Yogo\Nwould call a water demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:10.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We Yakoo, on the other hand,\Ncall it the spirit of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like I made\Nthe right call in coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:18.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torogai, can you do anything\Nto remove this egg or whatever it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:21.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:27.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The second queen asked me\Nthe very same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:36.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nayug and Sagu overlap,\Nsupporting each ether's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:40.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it is no simple matter\Nto interact between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:46.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If memory serves, in the Yakoo tongue,\NSagu means "this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:50.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, does Nayug\Nthen mean "the other world"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this is why I don't\Ncare much for amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When was the egg laid inside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no memory of it happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:06.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but strange things began to happen\Naround the beginning of spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:11.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If so, it must have been around\Nthe full moon of the first lunar month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You see, it is said that\NNayug and Sagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...are powerfully drawn to\Neach other during full moons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:24.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torugaru slew a water spirit\Nto create this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now his descendant\Nbears the egg of one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:31.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and is at risk of being killed by\Nhis own father because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:34.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that Nyunga Ro lm was foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:39.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Laying its egg inside a prince would\Nso clearly put the egg in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:44.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, how does it feel to be\Na Nyunga Ro Chaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torogai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:50.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...would you mind explaining things\Nin terms that we can all understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:54.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, the rest of us\Naren't schooled in the arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was tactfully put.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:06:00.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, I'll explain it so that\Neven a nitwit could understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Translated into the tongue of Yogo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:07.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Nyunga Ro Chaga would\Nmean "guardian of the spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian of the spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:16.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, it refers to the person\Nwho has been given the duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:20.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...of safeguarding the egg\Nuntil it hatches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But look what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But wait a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:35.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do not feel well.\NI shall go get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanda, I am going to the Knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:52.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Knot? The place where\NNayug and Sagu intersect?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:57.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I connect with the Water Folk\Nand have a proper discussion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I think things are\Ngoing to get quite nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to set out at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to set out at once!\NWith all due respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:08.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Balsa is injured,\Nand if I leave with you, she might...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you saying\Nthat you can't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:17.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose we can't have\Nthe egg fall into the mikado's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is your plan, Balsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:23.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been mulling that over\Nfor a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the fact that no pursuers\Nhave followed us here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:30.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...the mikado must have chosen a\Ndifferent means of capturing Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:38.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The men I fought were likely\Nthe mikado's first, most powerful card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean those youngsters\Nin the black outfits?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:46.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they paid me a little visit as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I beat them at their own game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:54.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you should be. So what would be\Nthe mikado's next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:08:01.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. What if he told everyone\Nthat Chagum died in the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:04.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably kept\Nhis activities secret so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:08.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but this might free him up\Nto take more forceful action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of forceful action?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:19.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Do you feel sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:23.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you touch him, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torogai doesn't mince any words,\Nbut she's a powerful magic weaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that she'll\Nfind a way to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:41.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy doesn't have the least\Nbit of talent for magic weaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:44.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but he's making fine progress\Nwhen it comes to treating injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because a certain\Ntomboy was always...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...covered in bumps and bruises\Never since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter. But what\Ndo you plan to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look after His Highness out there\Nfor the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Jiguro did for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:08.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not such a bad sentiment\Nto try to save the lives of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:14.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to appease the souls lost\Nin the process of saving your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, how many lives\Nhave you saved so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could we please drop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many lives have you taken\Nfor those you've saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:31.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The lives of ten people?\NTwenty people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or has it been fifty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I left this place, not one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you'd had\Na fight with Tanda over that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that you left here\Ntwo years ago, as I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:04.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa. What you think of the\Nlives of others is entirely up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:08.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in this one instance,\Nyou might not have that luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:12.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If, as the legends say,\Nthat egg hatches into a water spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:16.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it's highly likely that this land\Nwill be struck by a terrible drought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:20.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, the number of lives\Nyou carry on your shoulders...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:24.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...will include the millions of Yogo\Nand Yakoo people who live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:29.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still insist on protecting\Nthe prince with those lives at stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save him, and see\Nwhat I can do about the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a hopeless fool you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be safe if you stay inside the hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:56.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It sounds like it's a wolf\Nthat's strayed from its pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:59.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen to\Nwhat I'm about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Due to my current condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm going to divide up some jobs\Nthat I want you to do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If things work out\Naccording to my plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:13.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll be able to throw\Nour pursuers completely off our trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:18.97,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was\Ngoing to split up the work...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so why are Saya and I\Nthe only ones getting kicked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call this being kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:33.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be laying low\Nin Yashiro Village for a while, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:37.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle's house is there.\NRelax. Balsa won't steer you wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:43.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but we'd do anything\Nfor Balsa! Come hell or high water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:46.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She shouldn't be so protective of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:01.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, you haven't heard?\NIt's a manhunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:04.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The call suddenly came\Ndown from the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:05.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A manhunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:08.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that fire that\Nkilled the prince at Ninomiya Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:09.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:14.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Word has it that the fire was set\Nby some woman from Kanbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was Balsa\Nor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:24.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, they said that the\Nmanhunt forces are mobilizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...tomorrow morning to capture her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:30.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're covering all ground from\Nthe Torinaki River to Yashiro Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:48.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:52.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see it. If they're conscripting\Neven the farmers from this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...this manhunt will be more\Nthan one or two hundred strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:59.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two go back to the hut.\NTell Balsa what's happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NThis is exactly what you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Saya, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:14.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Chamber of the Epistles,\Nfrom which even the mikado is barred...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient Yogo script...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are all epistles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:22.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. They're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:50.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're in mourning today,\Nso we aren't conducting any business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies. I'm aware of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but I was told that if I came here,\Nyou would hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hear you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Forgive me if this seems abrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but this establishment is\Nknown as the Blue Hand, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:12.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, if I might ask,\Nwhere did you hear that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, from an acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:20.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what is the name of this\Nacquaintance of yours, if you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind at all. Her name is Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:26.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa the Spear-wielder? That Balsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:36.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you! What's your\Nconnection to that spear-wielder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:40.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on your story,\Nyou might not walk out of here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:45.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, what business does\NBalsa the Spear-wielder have with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:50.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she says that she wants to\Nbuy all of your merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:53.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's hardly unusual, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curse that woman!\NIs she out of her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time after time she's\Nhindered our business...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and now she wants to buy from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:04.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?\NYou're a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so upset by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:09.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does it always upset you to have\Nsomeone buy your merchandise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:10.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You keep casually throwing around\Nthe word "merchandise."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:18.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what sort of\Nmerchandise we deal in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't told that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our business dealings center around\Nthe buying and selling of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:32.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that means that our\Nstock in trade is human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so calm about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:41.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The manhunt forces won't get started\Nuntil tomorrow morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but we're talking about\Nsome serious forces out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:49.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. If they all\Ncame at us at once, we'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We hear that it was you who\Nreduced Ninomiya Palace to ashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:18.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and now you want to buy people\Nfrom us with palace crest gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care to explain yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:31.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can pay you back for all\Nyou've done to us right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? And do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:36.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the palace, treasure in hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:44.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's talk business.\NHow's your stock looking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got 30 people on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A few of them are Yogo natives.\NThe rest are foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I'll take them\Nall off your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:59.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?\NWhat the hell are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:05.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those gems are your payment.\NI trust you'll be able to circulate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:11.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those gems represent\Na mother's love for her child!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:16.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly aware of that.\NThat's why this is the time to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deliver them all to you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:26.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be necessary.\NJust unlock the door to your hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:31.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning, set free\Nall of the people you're holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:35.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the end of your duties.\NIsn't that an easy job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:39.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it. I can tell what you're up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This should be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:47.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to cause no end of trouble\Nfor the manhunt forces, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:50.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've gotten\Nsmarter over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:55.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But listen, if you recapture the people\Nyou've freed, you'll pay dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:58.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can trust us. This is business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:03.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't pry into what you've done,\Nbut come back when it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:07.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure,\Nlet's team up and get rich together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let's not even joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:21.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't part of the deal,\Nbut that horse of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:23.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the sound of its hooves,\Nis it a Kokkou stallion...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:27.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...said to be able to gallop across\Nthree kingdoms in a single night?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have sharp ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:32.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much.\NThen I'll help myself to the horse too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:38.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!\NThat's one order I can't fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me for this, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:57.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's Balsa for you! She's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:07.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you want to\Nget something off your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:11.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just thinking to myself\Nthat you're as amazing as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:19.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For as long as I've known you,\Nyou've always been self-reliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:21.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:24.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...at times like this, you should\Nask me for help, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:13.02,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:20.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.16,0:23:25.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.43,0:23:32.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:47.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:56.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:24:03.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:08.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:16.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:20.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.92,0:24:29.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.16,0:24:39.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:45.28,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:44.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The secret plan is a success...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.41,0:24:46.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and Balsa slips past the manhunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.82,0:24:48.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, it appeared that she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.85,0:24:52.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\N"To Die in the Misty Blue."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.99,0:24:56.99,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6\NTo Die in the Misty Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.95,0:24:56.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two bodies vanish into the ravine...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.06,0:24:56.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Die in the Misty Blue
